requirements:
  - Create tracking-screen/components/ folder housing TrackingPlayerControls.tsx, TrackingRouteMap.tsx, TrackingSummaryPanel.tsx.
  - Move playback timers and refs into hooks/useTrackingPlayback.ts with single interval lifecycle.
